bassi search bassi years in charge bassi srl are now an integral part of the sevcon group of companies supplying some of the worlds leading companies with electrification solutions with over  years’ experience in creating innovative battery charging and power supplies bassi offer technology enabled products to satisfy the worlds increasing demand for fast opportunity charging for all battery chemistries used in industrial commercial and passenger vehicles scroll down why sevcon why choose sevcon your electrification partner sevcon is at the forefront of the ongoing global transition from fossil fuels to clean energy from internal combustion engines to hybrid and electric vehicles we have been designing and manufacturing highquality motor controllers and system components for a variety of hybrid and electric vehicles for over half a century our partners range from leading onroad vehicle manufacturers to forklift truck and electric motorcycle makers in choosing sevcon you can be confident you will be working with an innovative and responsive business one with a cando attitude and unrivalled experience in delivering highquality electrification solutions our history our management team quality  environment our products high voltage controllers sevcons family of high voltage controllers cover the voltage ranges v to over v dc and power levels from kw to kw view product type low voltage controllers the family of low voltage controllers cover the voltage ranges from v to v dc with their high reliability and compact dimensions our dc motor controllers are used on both pump and traction applications in some of the worlds leading material handling vehicles view product type dcdc converters sevcon offer a comprehensive range of converters covering battery voltages from v to over v and output voltages from  to v as power demands increase you will find products that can satisfy power needs from w through to kw view product type battery chargers through the bassi brand sevcon supply a wide range of battery chargers and power management devices for both industrial onvehicle and automotive applications the voltage ranges from  to v and power levels up to kw view product type accessories to support the range of motor controllers and chargers sevcon offers a range of electronic gauges displays and other components view product type custom made sevcon has over half a century of experience designing innovative motor controllers used by some of the most demanding customers throughout the world view product type search for a product search our solutions sevcon doesn’t stop at just supplying innovative marketleading products customers keep coming back to sevcon because we offer worldclass application support to ensure our customers get the most out of our products working closely with our customers we often understand and have already experienced the challenges you face in implementing electrification technology here are some of the solutions we have helped deliver to our customers view our solutions scroll down news and events record year at sevcon read more  record year at sevcon  an ambitious growth strategy  sevcon motor controller is part of hovercraft project view all news  cenex low carbon vehicle event   electric and hybrid vehicle expo europe   inter battery  view all events scroll down contact us share this page contact sevcon interested in choosing sevcon as your electrification partner contact us today name company your city email address telephone united kingdom usa germany france japan south korea china australia spain italy belgium canada other message submit enquiry prefer to speak to us directly find contacts   bassi holding votes for sevcon board’s director nominees and charter amendment urges ryan morrismeson capital to stop dissident proxy campaign nasdaqsev english français register sign in bassi holding votes for sevcon board’s director nominees and charter amendment urges ryan morrismeson capital to stop dissident proxy campaign january    et  source sevcon inc lugo italy jan   globe newswire  bassi holding srl – a significant stockholder in sevcon inc nasdaqsev owning  of sevcon’s outstanding shares – announced today that it has voted its shares “for all” the sevcon board’s nominees for election at the annual meeting of stockholders to be held on february   and “for” the charter amendment proposed for that meeting the bassi family urges dissident director ryan morris and meson capital partners to stop their disruptive proxy campaign against sevcon  the bassis believe that the current board and management are pursuing the best course to create longterm value for sevcon’s stockholders including bassi holding and that continuing with a divisive proxy fight is wasteful and counterproductive  importantly the bassis reject ryan morris’s assertions that he is responsible for sevcon’s forwardlooking strategy or that he could improve on it “we accepted sevcon shares when we sold our company to sevcon because we have great faith in the current board’s strategy and we continue to support it we believe that giving mr morris a position of control would be a step backwards and bad for the stockholders” “we are confident that the current sevcon board is on the right path a continued proxy campaign by mr morris and meson capital will only draw resources away from the board’s focus on increasing stockholder value we urge mr morris to do the right thing for stockholders and withdraw the proxy campaign now” about sevconsevcon is a global supplier of control and power solutions for zeroemission electric and hybrid vehicles its products control on and offroad vehicle speed and movement integrate specialized functions optimize energy consumption and help reduce air pollution sevcon’s bassi division produces battery chargers for electric vehicles power management and uninterrupted power source systems for industrial medical and telecom applications and electronic instrumentation for battery laboratories the company supplies customers from its operations in the us uk france germany italy china and the asia pacific region as well as through an international dealer network learn more about sevcon at wwwsevconcom important additional informationsevcon inc seven of its directors and its executive officers and marvin g schorr are participants in the solicitation of proxies from company stockholders in connection with the matters to be considered at the companys  annual meeting  sevcon has filed a definitive proxy statement and white proxy card with the securities and exchange commission “sec” in connection with such solicitation  company stockholders are strongly encouraged to read the definitive proxy statement and accompanying white proxy card as they contain important information  information regarding the identity of the participants and their direct or indirect interests by security holdings or otherwise is set forth in the proxy statement and other materials filed with the sec  shareholders can obtain any proxy statement any amendments or supplements to the proxy statement and other documents filed by the company with the sec for no charge at the secs website at wwwsecgov by request to sevcon inc  northboro road southborough ma  attn corporate secretary telephone   or from the companys website httpirsevconcomseccfmcontacts matt boyle president and ceo     mattboylesevconcom matt goldfarb chairman of the board   related articles other press releases by sevcon inc sevcon signs definitive agreement to be acquired by borgwarner july    sevcon acquires remaining  equity interest in chinese joint venture june    sevcon reports financial results for second quarter fiscal  may    sevcon to announce secondquarter  financial results on may  may    sevcon to present at the microcap conference march    profile sevcon inc   subscribe via rss  subscribe via atom  javascript southborough massachusetts united states   httpwwwtechopssevconcom contact data contacts matt boyle president a